I manage to make it work:
First download and install the latest hasp driver from http://www.aladdin.com/support/hasp/enduser.asp
Install the Alldata program from CD.
Copy from CD the file in \crack to Alldata directory and run it.
After this, when u start the program u will be asked for some codes, just click ok.
And, voila! Working!
